      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, tear your <strong>chestnut mushrooms</strong> into the pan and cook for 3 min or until beginning to soften</p><p>Tip: Try not to stir the mushrooms too often, as this will stop them from caramelising!</p>",
